{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_10_02",
  "title": "白石沙季",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――探訪番組ロケの三時間前",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "スケジュールを調整していただいて\nありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 4.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ロケの開始時間を後ろ倒しに出来て良かったよ\n本当は前日とかにしたかったんだが……",
      "startTime": 9.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.1333331704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、むしろ直前の方が下見の経験を\nすぐに本番に活かせますから問題ありません",
      "startTime": 16.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.3999998371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "あらかじめ料理や地理は把握していますが\nやはり実際に歩くのとは勝手が違いますから",
      "startTime": 23.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "まずはどこから行きたい？\n沙季の好きな所からでいいぞ",
      "startTime": 30,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.2666665037
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "では、まずは神社に行きましょうか\nこの町で最も由緒ある場所らしいですから",
      "startTime": 36.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "何事もまずは雰囲気から、と言いますからね",
      "startTime": 39.6333331704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――神社",
      "startTime": 44.3333331704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.3333331704
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.3333331704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "この神社は創建されてから千年以上の年月が\n経過しているらしいです",
      "startTime": 50.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛成就の神様が祀られていることから\n沢山の人でいつも賑わっているそうですよ",
      "startTime": 55.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.6666665037
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "凄く詳しいな\nまるで本物のガイドさんみたいだ",
      "startTime": 61.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "事前にロケ地の勉強をしてきましたから\n案内をするぐらいであれば問題ありません",
      "startTime": 67,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.0999998371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、恋愛についての勉強もしてきましたよ\n今回の鬼門はそこでしたから",
      "startTime": 74.299598095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.2666665037
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……ちなみに、どんなことを勉強してきたのか\n一応聞かせてもらってもいいか？",
      "startTime": 80.3565605998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "これは渚ちゃんから借りた少女漫画に\n載っていたのですが……",
      "startTime": 85.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.8999998371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "なんでも、人は相手から「おもしれーやつ」と\n言われると心がときめいてしまうらしいです",
      "startTime": 91.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.0666665037
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "他にも、壁に追いやられた状態であごを掴まれたら\nドキドキしてしまうとも書かれていました",
      "startTime": 100.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "これは壁ドンと呼ばれているらしいです\n行為に対して名前が少々物騒ですよね……",
      "startTime": 108.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.5333331704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "つまり、恋愛とはどれだけ相手を翻弄出来るかに\nかかっていると言っても過言ではないということです",
      "startTime": 116.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛においてシチュエーションが大事だとは\nよく言うから、あながち間違ってもいないのか……？",
      "startTime": 123.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.8333331704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "少女漫画の他にも、平安時代あたりの恋についても\n勉強してきたのですが……",
      "startTime": 132.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、百人一首の五十二番にて\n藤原道信はこんな和歌を詠んでいます",
      "startTime": 138.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.8333331704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "「明けぬれば暮るるものとは知りながら\nなほ恨めしき朝ぼらけかな」",
      "startTime": 145.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.8333331704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "これは、恋人と別れなければならない夜明けなんて\n嫌いだ、という意味の和歌なのですが……",
      "startTime": 152.1613918208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "翌日も会えるはずなのに残念だなぁなどと思って\nしまうのは、どうしてだろうと考えてしまいまして……",
      "startTime": 159.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.4666665037
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "愛する者同士、たとえ短い時間であろうとも\n離れたくないと思ってるからじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 167.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……確かに、ネットで読んだ記事にも\n恋人とは常に一緒にいたいものだと書かれていました",
      "startTime": 174.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.6999998371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "でも、昔の人は恋人以外の相手とも恋愛関係に\nなることが多かったみたいなんです",
      "startTime": 184.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、在原業平は妻がいながら三千人以上の女性と\n恋をしたと言われているそうで……",
      "startTime": 191.9999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 194.8999988198
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski023.m4a",
      "text": "これは、不倫というシチュエーションを大事に\nしているということなのでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 198.1939837223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_02-ski024.m4a",
      "text": "もしそうなのだとしたら……\nさ、さすがにハレンチ過ぎると思います！",
      "startTime": 204.3666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 208.6999988198
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
